Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.58,0:22:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All the souls that you could meet on the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,translation Mu_Cool
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,hitotsu datte machigai janai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.37,0:22:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,certainly it was pure and innocent,
